<?xml version="1.0" encoding="utf-8"?>
<ScrollView xmlns:android="http://schemas.android.com/apk/res/android"
    xmlns:app="http://schemas.android.com/apk/res-auto"
    xmlns:tools="http://schemas.android.com/tools"
    android:layout_width="match_parent"
    android:layout_height="match_parent"
    >

    <LinearLayout
        android:id="@+id/linearLayout7"
        android:layout_width="match_parent"
        android:layout_height="match_parent"
        android:background="#FFFFFF"
        android:orientation="vertical"
        app:layout_constraintBottom_toBottomOf="parent"
        app:layout_constraintEnd_toEndOf="parent"
        app:layout_constraintStart_toStartOf="parent"
        app:layout_constraintTop_toTopOf="parent">

        <TextView
            android:layout_width="wrap_content"
            android:layout_height="wrap_content"
            android:layout_marginBottom="2dp"
            android:layout_marginTop="15dp"
            android:layout_gravity="center"
            android:background="#C0F4E2"
            android:text="About E-Voting"
            android:textColor="#000"
            android:textSize="25dp"
            android:textStyle="bold" />

        <LinearLayout
                android:layout_width="match_parent"
                android:layout_height="1dp"
                android:background="#5C5C5C"
                android:layout_marginTop="4dp">

        </LinearLayout>

        <TextView
                android:layout_width="match_parent"
                android:layout_height="wrap_content"
                android:layout_marginBottom="1dp"
                android:layout_marginLeft="13dp"
                android:layout_marginTop="15dp"
                android:text="We are building this application with an aim that one-day Indian elections would solely be conducted on this application. There would no polling booths, no election rallies and no election campaigning on roads. We hope that our idea will shape a discrimination-free, an inexpensive, steady and secure elections."
                android:textColor="#3E3E3E"
                android:textSize="18sp"
                />

        <TextView
                android:layout_width="wrap_content"
                android:layout_height="wrap_content"
                android:layout_marginBottom="2dp"
                android:layout_marginLeft="13dp"
                android:layout_marginTop="15dp"
                android:text="The salient features of this application would be:"
                android:textColor="#000"
                android:background="#C0F4E2"
                android:textSize="23sp"
                android:textStyle="bold" />

        <LinearLayout
                android:layout_width="match_parent"
                android:layout_height="1dp"
                android:background="#5C5C5C"
                android:layout_marginTop="4dp">

        </LinearLayout>

        <TextView
                android:layout_width="match_parent"
                android:layout_height="wrap_content"
                android:layout_marginBottom="2dp"
                android:layout_marginLeft="13dp"
                android:layout_marginTop="15dp"
                android:text="1. Parties can easily and securely broadcast their election posters and videos into the application. Parties can also conduct live public meetings with the complete involvement of the electors through a chat system."
                android:textColor="#3E3E3E"
                android:textSize="18sp"
                />

        <TextView
                android:layout_width="match_parent"
                android:layout_height="wrap_content"
                android:layout_marginBottom="2dp"
                android:layout_marginLeft="13dp"
                android:layout_marginTop="15dp"
                android:text="2. There will be real-time monitoring over shared content to bring about a check over the caste-based campaigning."
                android:textColor="#3E3E3E"
                android:textSize="18sp"
                />

        <TextView
                android:layout_width="match_parent"
                android:layout_height="wrap_content"
                android:layout_marginBottom="2dp"
                android:layout_marginLeft="13dp"
                android:layout_marginTop="15dp"
                android:text="3. There would be an easy and secure way of casting a vote through the application using Blockchain. The voterâ€™s information will be stored in a Block so that they are not easily tampered by the attackers."
                android:textColor="#3E3E3E"
                android:textSize="18sp"
                />

        <TextView
                android:layout_width="match_parent"
                android:layout_height="wrap_content"
                android:layout_marginBottom="2dp"
                android:layout_marginLeft="13dp"
                android:layout_marginTop="15dp"
                android:text="4. Using Blockchain, we promise a steady and secure election system. The election results could be calculated steadily and securely."
                android:textColor="#3E3E3E"
                android:textSize="18sp"
                />

        <TextView
                android:layout_width="match_parent"
                android:layout_height="wrap_content"
                android:layout_marginBottom="2dp"
                android:layout_marginLeft="13dp"
                android:layout_marginTop="15dp"
                android:text="5. In a place where there is no internet, the application can build a local blockchain, storing data in the phone memory and can be later merged to the global blockchain. (Again at such places election will be conducted under supervised authority)"
                android:textColor="#3E3E3E"
                android:textSize="18sp"
                />

    </LinearLayout>


</ScrollView>